{"id": 2280, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在童话故事里都发现了哪些不易察觉的刻板印象设定？", "description": "公主王子带来的不光是公主病杰克苏，还有女孩子都应该是小公主，男孩子就得历经险阻变勇者的刻板印象。（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 3495, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180412163928a2xWcAblXRrz95oT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 275712, "content": "角色只拥有好的品质或坏的品质，而不是多面的存在", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867637}, {"id": 275713, "content": "从此幸福的生活在一起。。。恩？？？！！然后呢。。然后呢。。咋没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314763}, {"id": 275969, "content": "有的人活着，他已经死了；\r\n有的人死了，他还活着。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178173}, {"id": 275716, "content": "很多个童话故事中的王子是同一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733560}, {"id": 276484, "content": "配角不好过,,Ծ^Ծ,,", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310993}, {"id": 276485, "content": "配角不好过,,Ծ^Ծ,,", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310993}, {"id": 275718, "content": "主角的正义光环", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015593}, {"id": 275719, "content": "公主不会爱上大坏蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314842}, {"id": 275720, "content": "公主都美丽，王子都英俊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314864}, {"id": 275722, "content": "故事的最好都是美好的结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314875}, {"id": 275978, "content": "女主总是善良的过头，男主总是喜欢傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236175}, {"id": 275725, "content": "最后幸福的生活在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 110}, {"id": 275727, "content": "误会论", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310072}, {"id": 275728, "content": "王子和公主永远幸福的生活在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312774}, {"id": 275729, "content": "大灰狼永远是坏蛋，小白兔是傻白甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304435}, {"id": 275730, "content": "总是救来救去的剧情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314014}, {"id": 275732, "content": "美德总是能战胜丑恶，世界似乎永远向善，向着人类的善。即使大自然总是不带任何感情色彩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311665}, {"id": 275733, "content": "童话故事里都是骗人的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118986}, {"id": 275735, "content": "幸福和快乐的结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 276503, "content": "剧本都是那个套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319707}, {"id": 275736, "content": "坏女巫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315125}, {"id": 276505, "content": "往往你以为最有可能帮你的，偏偏最让你心寒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279453}, {"id": 275740, "content": "故事的女主角们最后都成了公主?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315152}, {"id": 275741, "content": "公主一般都不是亲生母亲养大的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315155}, {"id": 275743, "content": "出身决定论", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743793}, {"id": 275744, "content": "女主的爸爸总是一个无能的失语者...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 288555}, {"id": 275745, "content": "公主都有主角光环，永远闪亮登场，永远死不了\n获得爱情就是结局了?\n这样真的不会成为下一个故事的继母吗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315258}, {"id": 276513, "content": "红黄蓝（三原色）是主角配色。\n绿紫橙（三间色）是反派配色。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318090}, {"id": 275746, "content": "为什么龙会看守公主？龙不是看守宝藏的么？还是说公主也是宝藏的一种？算不算物化女性，嗯？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795586}, {"id": 278821, "content": "你的善良总有人发现，你的善良终有回报，真爱的几率无限大，看到即遇到，遇到即永远，所有的感情都被祝福", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1330712}, {"id": 275752, "content": "公主都是善良、青春、活泼可爱的，皇后都很恶毒！哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315340}, {"id": 275754, "content": "一眼看到结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315306}, {"id": 275755, "content": "主角光环永远保佑不死", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311176}, {"id": 276523, "content": "哇哇哇", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319791}, {"id": 275756, "content": "通话里王子必定是和公主在一起的人 但通话必定是通话 很多骑白马的不一定是王子 也行是青蛙变王子也说不定", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315342}, {"id": 275762, "content": "过于绝对的善恶好坏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315530}, {"id": 275763, "content": "反派一般很聪明，智商碾压主角。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315132}, {"id": 275765, "content": "最小的公主总是最美丽可爱聪明善良的那个，大公主和二公主不是没有她美丽就是没她善良，或者比她蠢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315606}, {"id": 275766, "content": "硌着公主的那粒豆子可真大。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315631}, {"id": 275767, "content": "都没有kiss 的桥段?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315639}, {"id": 275771, "content": "一般都会有美好的结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315736}, {"id": 275776, "content": "王子生下来就是为了娶公主这件事浪费了青春受尽了磨难最后娶完了就么屁事干了 连个自己的爱好也没有?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315754}, {"id": 275781, "content": "所以说 耽美bl纯爱童话比这些欧洲传统真实多了  还不如给孩子讲纯爱故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202912}, {"id": 275784, "content": "结婚了一定幸福", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255823}, {"id": 275786, "content": "女主可以是公主、灰姑娘（一定要美），但男主必定是现在王子或者以后成为王子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316035}, {"id": 275787, "content": "不说贵族就是贫民……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 275789, "content": "只有绝对的对错，对错中间的灰色地带消失了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1304443}, {"id": 275793, "content": "结局就是公主和王子幸福的生活在一起了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316276}, {"id": 275794, "content": "结局就是公主和王子幸福的生活在一起了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1316276}, {"id": 275540, "content": "好人总会有好结局，坏人总会收到惩罚，有情人终成眷属，受难者得到声张，总会有人来救你，你的苦难委屈所有人都知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 368, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313390}]}